confOf#Trip: The Social Event is the parent of the Banquet and the Working Event. It is also the child of the Conference. The Social Event is also the parent of the Conference.
confOf#Banquet: The Social Event is the parent event of the Banquet. It is followed by the Administrative event which is followed by the Working event. The event has the same topic as the Working event and is the parent event of the Banquet.
confOf#Reception: Reception is the parent of Social event which is a part of the Administrative event. The Social event is also part of the Administrative event which is a parallel event to the Reviewing results event.
confOf#Social_event: Social event is a child of Banquet and Reception.
confOf#Event: The registration of participants event is the parent event of the Administrative event. The event is also the child of the Working event which has the same topic.
confOf#Contribution: Contribution is a child of Paper which is the parent of Contribution. ContactEmail is the email address of Contribution.
confOf#City: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Organization: The City Organization is a child of the Company which is parented by the Organization.
confOf#Person: The person has the name Thing and the city.
confOf#Topic: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Country: The following table shows the percentage of people who are enrolled in the program.
confOf#Company: The parent company of the company is the Organization which is child of the company. The organization has Country.
confOf#University: The University is parented by the Organization which is a subsidiary of the Company. The University is also the parent of the Organization.
confOf#Scholar: Scholar is a parent of a person who studies at the University. Scholar is a child of an organization which is parented by a company. Company is parented by an organization which is the parent of the organization. Thing is a parent of the University.
confOf#Administrator: The administrator is the parent of the person who is the child of a Science Worker who is employed by the organization hasCity which is located in the country.
confOf#Poster: Poster is the parent of Contribution which is a child of Poster and Paper.
confOf#Paper: The author of the paper is the parent of Thing. The author is also the parent of Person who has a Country.
confOf#Short_paper: The short paper is the parent of Contribution which is the parent of Thing.
confOf#Reviewing_results_event: The Reviewing results event is parented by the Administrative event. The Social event is also a parented by the Administrative event. The Camera Ready event is also a parented by the Administrative event. The default choice for the event is Thing.
confOf#Administrative_event: Camera Ready is the parent of the Administrative event which is a parallel event to the Administrative event.
confOf#Reviewing_event: Reviewing event is parented by both Administrative event and Social event. The event is a child of both the Social event and the Working event. Thing is the default name of the event.
confOf#Registration_of_participants_even: The registration of participants event is parented by the Administrative event which is followed by the Social event which is also parented by the Working event. The reception event is also a child of the Social event which is also parented by the Administrative event.
confOf#Submission_event: The Submission event is parented by the Administrative event. The Social event is the child of the Reviewing event and the Working event is the child of the Tutorial event.
confOf#Camera_Ready_event: The camera ready event is the parent of the Administrative event which is followed by the Social event. The event is also the child of the Trip and is also the child of the Working event.
confOf#Workshop: Working event is parented by Conference and Administrative event. Workshop is parented by Conference and Administrative event.
confOf#Conference: Working event is parented by Conference and Social event. Conference is parented by Social event which is the default choice of Thing.
confOf#Tutorial: Working event is a child of Conference and Tutorial. It is also the parent of Working event.
confOf#Working_event: Working event is a child of Workshop and Conference. Working event is also a child of Conference.
confOf#Member: The Participant is the parent of the Participant and the child of Chair PC. The child of Chair PC is also the parent of Thing.
confOf#Participant: The Participant is a child of a Science Worker who is a citizen of the country.
confOf#Member_PC: The parent of a member of the PC is a person who is employed by the organization Thing. The organization hasCity and hasCountry.
confOf#Chair_PC: The Chair of the PC is the parent of a person who is a Science Worker. This person is a child of the member of the PC who is an expert on the topic.
confOf#Student: The student is the parent of the participant who has the Postal Code and the city of which they live.
confOf#Science_Worker: The parent of a Science Worker is the person who has the Postal Code and is the child of a Regular and a Regular.
confOf#Assistant: The Assistant is the parent of the Chair PC who is employed by the organization. The University is the parent of the Company which is the parent of the University.
confOf#Volunteer: The volunteer is the parent of the person who is the child of a Science Worker who is a member of the Member PC who is an expert on the topic.
confOf#Regular: The Participant is a member of the Regular family and is the parent of the Participant. The Participant is a member of the Regular family.
confOf#Author: The author is the parent of a person who has PostalCode and is a child of a member of the PC.
